  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.netbeans.jemmy.Outputable, org.netbeans.jemmy.Timeoutable

    public class SearchResultsOperator
extends TopComponentOperator
    Provides access to the "Search Results" view.

    Usage:

          SearchResultsOperator sro = new SearchResultsOperator();
      sro.openResult("MyClass|myMethod");

    Timeouts used:
    SearchResultsOperator.SearchTime - maximum time for search to be performed.
